description: You do not know anything, yet you have to move forward.  Wander through the corridors of a mysterious factory and recover your abilities.  Fight patroling drones and break through to demanding boss battles.  Seek a way out and find the meaning of the game's title.
name: fig.
intro: Who are you? A human or a robot? Where are you? Is this a factory? When are you? Is this a future or a present?
